com.netflix.spectator.controllers.model

Class ApplicationRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.spectator.controllers.model.ApplicationRegistry

  • public class ApplicationRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
    An ApplicationRegistry is the encoding of the metrics from a particular application. This is only public for testing purposes so implements equals but not hash.
